Class OntologyTermEnricherStatisticsWriter

  • java.lang.Object
    • psidev.psi.mi.jami.enricher.listener.impl.writer.EnricherStatisticsWriter<C>
      • psidev.psi.mi.jami.enricher.listener.impl.writer.CvTermEnricherStatisticsWriter<OntologyTerm>
        • psidev.psi.mi.jami.enricher.listener.impl.writer.OntologyTermEnricherStatisticsWriter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EventListener, CvTermEnricherListener<OntologyTerm>, EnricherListener<OntologyTerm>, OntologyTermEnricherListener, AliasesChangeListener<CvTerm>, AnnotationsChangeListener<CvTerm>, CvTermChangeListener, IdentifiersChangeListener<CvTerm>, OntologyTermChangeListener, XrefsChangeListener<CvTerm>
    public class OntologyTermEnricherStatisticsWriter
extends CvTermEnricherStatisticsWriter<OntologyTerm>
implements OntologyTermEnricherListener
    A statistics logger which records changes made by the enricher. Each addition, removal or update is counted and, upon the completion of the enrichment of the object, is logged in either a file of successes or failures depending on the enrichmentStatus.
    Since:
    18/07/13
    Author:
    Gabriel Aldam (galdam@ebi.ac.uk)
